stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> queued
  queued --> claimed: DEV worker lock
  claimed --> materializing_spec: validate target and dedupe
  materializing_spec --> ready_for_stage: spec created or attached
  materializing_spec --> blocked: invalid target or missing context
  ready_for_stage --> stage_active: stage registry entry created
  stage_active --> dev_done: reviewer complete
  stage_active --> failed: run failed after retries
  dev_done --> waiting_user_validation: evidence published
  waiting_user_validation --> approved_by_user: user approves
  waiting_user_validation --> stage_active: user requests fixes
  approved_by_user --> ready_for_dev_main: merge queue requested
  ready_for_dev_main --> integrating: serialized merge lock acquired
  integrating --> merged_to_dev_main: gates and integration pass
  integrating --> blocked: conflict or failed validation
  merged_to_dev_main --> ready_for_prod_promotion: release scope selected
  ready_for_prod_promotion --> promoting: promotion.run accepted
  promoting --> promoted_to_prod: promotion done
  promoting --> blocked: approval, drain, validation, or config gate
  promoting --> failed: deterministic step failed
  blocked --> stage_active: remediation in stage
  failed --> cancelled: operator closes item
  promoted_to_prod --> [*]
  cancelled --> [*]

